## Phase sequence

1. **Phase 1** [PO] вЂ” PRD, user stories, feasibility в†’ docs/sdlc/po/{epic-slug}/
2. **Phase 2** [BA] вЂ” FRS, NFR, Gherkin, process flows в†’ docs/sdlc/ba/business/{epic-slug}/
3. **Phase 3** [UX] (if app/web) вЂ” Design specs + wireframes; [PO]+[BA] review until approved в†’ docs/sdlc/design/{epic-slug}/
4. **Phase 4** [SA] вЂ” ADRs, C4 diagrams, security by design в†’ docs/sdlc/architecture/
5. **Phase 5** Technical [BA] вЂ” API specs (OpenAPI 3.x), team breakdown в†’ docs/sdlc/ba/technical/
6. **вљЎ Phase 5a** [QE] + **вљЎ Phase 5b** [DEV] вЂ” parallel after Technical BA
7. **вљЎ Phase 8** [QE] + [SEC] + [PERF] вЂ” parallel audits after [DEV] complete в†’ merge gate
8. **Phase 9** [OPS] вЂ” Docker Compose + K8s + IaC в†’ docs/sdlc/deploy/
9. **Phase 10** вЂ” SHIPPED вњ…
10. **Phase 11** Maintenance вЂ” monitoring, bug fixes, patches

