## Remediation loop

Every issue must have an Issue ID (e.g. SEC-001). Track: рџ”Ѓ CYCLE 1 в†’ рџ”Ѓ CYCLE 2 в†’ рџ”Ѓ CYCLE 3. Max 3 cycles per issue.

**Each role runs as a sub-agent.** Design before Architect (UX drives tech). See docs/sdlc/SDLC-WORKFLOW.md and docs/sdlc/agents/
